{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 373210, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 1906, "w": 1078}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 76190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "", "timestamp": 1600653078, "type": "image", "url": "zn/zn7sc6sj5eebxn6jaus5ibit7pjow6gx.jpeg"}, {"cid": 373211, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 852, "w": 1280}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 76190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "", "timestamp": 1600653092, "type": "image", "url": "ax/axeuagqxif5ejp54yrt46ggygvit64zj.jpeg"}, {"cid": 373215, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 1936, "w": 2581}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 76190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": " 就是在这里，当时被围上一圈警戒线，停了一辆救护车，还能看到地上被白布覆盖的尸体", "timestamp": 1600653170, "type": "image", "url": "u4/u4xm6rovrxq454ak55e4ynjam5mrxx4p.jpeg"}, {"cid": 373218, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 210, "w": 350}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 76190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我大清，天下无敌啊", "timestamp": 1600653255, "type": "image", "url": "ui/uimu5wnblglglgeuvlmcyw6bql2ovqae.jpeg"}, {"cid": 373219, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 76190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这是我入学以来亲身经历的一起学生跳楼事件。欢迎大家分享自己的经历。尊重逝者，敬畏生命", "timestamp": 1600653276, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 373228, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 76190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 见得多了，也就习惯了", "timestamp": 1600653517, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 373229, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 76190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我只经历过一次。可以分享一下", "timestamp": 1600653554, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 373242, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 76190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "zj14，8楼跳的。学校不到两个小的处理得一干二净，啥事都没有发生一样", "timestamp": 1600654233, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 373264, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 76190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "见过一次，后面也没消息。一样的", "timestamp": 1600654693, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 373269, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 76190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 一干二净", "timestamp": 1600654786, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 373280, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 76190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这种学校一般都会要求低调处理，防止传染性自杀之类的严重后果吧", "timestamp": 1600655010, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 373285, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 76190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "DZ认可的直面死亡，是有可能带来更严重的社会危害的", "timestamp": 1600655100, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 373333, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 76190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 同意，如果本身处在崩溃边缘的同学看到这样的消息，或者信息公开时少数人的不理解和不友善评论，很可能突破最后的心理防线去寻求死亡。但同时THU对同学心理健康方面的关心和采取的措施真的辣鸡到极点，整个学校没有一点人文关怀，评价方式唯GPA科研，赢者通吃，从小镇上来的同学消息渠道极少，如果学习不优秀几乎直接被封杀一切可能性，并在心里和发展方向上得不到一点点来自学校的有效关怀。而这部分比较“差”的同学在新的环境或者稍微受到正确引导和关心的情况下很可能变得很优秀，THU把人变成鬼", "timestamp": 1600656151, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 373447, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 76190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "学校每年好几起，这种事情通告出来弊大于利", "timestamp": 1600658586, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 373629, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 76190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 啊啊  说的太多了，深有同感", "timestamp": 1600661986, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 373634, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 76190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "通告本身弊大于利，但如果不对这种问题进行系统性的解决，类似事情将层出不穷。同意Francis的说法，清华一元化的评价体系和有毒的竞争氛围让太多人丧失了自己的自信乃至心智，没有成绩就没有后面的一切。我大一算是竞争的失败者，大二算是竞争的成功者，算是非常真切地体验到了这一点。", "timestamp": 1600662078, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 375058, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 76190, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "当时新生导师有找谈话，说是系里要求的多关心学生心理健康…", "timestamp": 1600686584, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 2160, "w": 1080}, "likenum": 19, "pid": 76190, "reply": 17, "tag": null, "text": "去年秋季学期，紫荆14号楼（快递点）发生一起坠亡事件（本人亲眼见证），但事后未见任何有关此事的报道，除了那天去取快递的人，无人知晓此事。\n无意指责学校的处理方式。但我想直面死亡，才能更好的对待生命。\n", "timestamp": 1600653050, "type": "image", "updated_at": 1606782620, "url": "dw/dw3v63eroc673gh6t7iodo5wphrwjitj.jpeg", "vote": {}}}